I’d like to pre-populate a field value in my embed code.

The docs make it look simple but clearly, I’m missing a step. My code is below.
_(And if I’m in the wrong channel, let me know!)_

```&lt;script charset="utf-8" type="text/javascript" src="//js.hsforms.net/forms/embed/v2.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
hbspt.forms.create({
    region: "na1",
    portalId: "4953342",
    formId: "199798c1-5fb0-4410-825b-25823fd196e3"
    onFormReady: function($form, ctx) {
        // Correctly use jQuery to select and check the radio button
        jQuery('input[name="issue_type"][value="SUPPORT"]').prop('checked', true).change();
    }
});
&lt;/script```
